data.description: Back on market at no fault of seller! Low-maintenance living in an intimate community minutes from Historic Downtown Monroe.  Fieldstone is made up of single-family homes and several duplex-style townhomes.  This home has 3 Bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a 2 car garage on the main level with a private 4th BR/Bonus with full bath up. This one has fresh paint throughout in a neutral color, new neutral carpet and hardwood flooring welcome you in the foyer & kitchen area.  The kitchen is spacious with a peninsula island breakfast bar and dining area.  The great room has soaring vaulted ceilings with a fireplace and architectural niche. The fenced yard and view of the trees offer a private relaxing area to hang out. HOA covers exterior, lawn maintenance, and irrigation. City covers refuse pickup. Monroe has so much to offer from eateries, coffee shops, boutiques, and breweries.  This property is move-in ready so make your appointment today!  monroenc.org/Community/Things-to-Do/Downtown-Monroe
